{
  "title": "Deletion of data in Outlook (possible recovery)",
  "slug": "deletion-of-data-in-outlook-possible-recovery",
  "categorySlug": "organisational-roll-out",
  "html": "<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell \" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-1 dnd-section kb-article-row-0-padding\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell dnd-column\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-2 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-2\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-3 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h1 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">Deletion of data in Outlook (possible recovery)</h1>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-4 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h2 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">Data that is deleted goes into the deleted items folder in Outlook.</h2>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-5 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_richtext_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_richtext_field\"><p>If you want to find the data that has been deleted using Data&amp;More's compliance solution, you need to go into \"Deleted Items\", where you have the option to restore the deleted data. The length of time that you can restore data depends on your organization's setup, but typically it is 30 days.</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"319\" style=\"height: auto; width: 688px;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-24-2023-10-12-17-9006-AM.png?width=688&amp;height=319&amp;name=image-png-Aug-24-2023-10-12-17-9006-AM.png\" width=\"688\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-24-2023-10-12-17-9006-AM.png?width=344&amp;height=160&amp;name=image-png-Aug-24-2023-10-12-17-9006-AM.png 344w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-24-2023-10-12-17-9006-AM.png?width=688&amp;height=319&amp;name=image-png-Aug-24-2023-10-12-17-9006-AM.png 688w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-24-2023-10-12-17-9006-AM.png?width=1032&amp;height=479&amp;name=image-png-Aug-24-2023-10-12-17-9006-AM.png 1032w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-24-2023-10-12-17-9006-AM.png?width=1376&amp;height=638&amp;name=image-png-Aug-24-2023-10-12-17-9006-AM.png 1376w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-24-2023-10-12-17-9006-AM.png?width=1720&amp;height=798&amp;name=image-png-Aug-24-2023-10-12-17-9006-AM.png 1720w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-24-2023-10-12-17-9006-AM.png?width=2064&amp;height=957&amp;name=image-png-Aug-24-2023-10-12-17-9006-AM.png 2064w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 688px) 100vw, 688px\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>When you click the text marked in red, you can restore the deleted emails.</p>\n<p><img class=\"hs-image-align-none\" height=\"232\" style=\"width: 688px; height: auto;\" src=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-24-2023-10-13-17-5565-AM.png?width=688&amp;height=232&amp;name=image-png-Aug-24-2023-10-13-17-5565-AM.png\" width=\"688\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-24-2023-10-13-17-5565-AM.png?width=344&amp;height=116&amp;name=image-png-Aug-24-2023-10-13-17-5565-AM.png 344w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-24-2023-10-13-17-5565-AM.png?width=688&amp;height=232&amp;name=image-png-Aug-24-2023-10-13-17-5565-AM.png 688w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-24-2023-10-13-17-5565-AM.png?width=1032&amp;height=348&amp;name=image-png-Aug-24-2023-10-13-17-5565-AM.png 1032w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-24-2023-10-13-17-5565-AM.png?width=1376&amp;height=464&amp;name=image-png-Aug-24-2023-10-13-17-5565-AM.png 1376w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-24-2023-10-13-17-5565-AM.png?width=1720&amp;height=580&amp;name=image-png-Aug-24-2023-10-13-17-5565-AM.png 1720w, https://support.dataandmore.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image-png-Aug-24-2023-10-13-17-5565-AM.png?width=2064&amp;height=696&amp;name=image-png-Aug-24-2023-10-13-17-5565-AM.png 2064w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 688px) 100vw, 688px\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>Restoring Deleted Data in OneDrive (for Business):</h3>\n<h4 data-start=\"244\" data-end=\"290\">1. <strong data-start=\"252\" data-end=\"290\">From Recycle Bin (within 93 days):</strong></h4>\n<ul data-start=\"291\" data-end=\"458\">\n<li data-start=\"291\" data-end=\"333\">\n<p data-start=\"293\" data-end=\"333\">Go to your <strong data-start=\"304\" data-end=\"332\">OneDrive (web interface)</strong>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"334\" data-end=\"375\">\n<p data-start=\"336\" data-end=\"375\">Click <strong data-start=\"342\" data-end=\"357\">Recycle bin</strong> in the left pane.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"376\" data-end=\"426\">\n<p data-start=\"378\" data-end=\"426\">Select the files or folders you want to restore.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"427\" data-end=\"458\">\n<p data-start=\"429\" data-end=\"458\">Click <strong data-start=\"435\" data-end=\"446\">Restore</strong> at the top.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote data-start=\"460\" data-end=\"562\">\n<p data-start=\"462\" data-end=\"562\">Files are retained in the Recycle Bin for <strong data-start=\"507\" data-end=\"518\">93 days</strong> by default (unless the admin changes this).</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h4 data-start=\"564\" data-end=\"629\">2. <strong data-start=\"572\" data-end=\"629\">Second-Stage Recycle Bin (if not found in first bin):</strong></h4>\n<ul data-start=\"630\" data-end=\"755\">\n<li data-start=\"630\" data-end=\"703\">\n<p data-start=\"632\" data-end=\"703\">At the bottom of the Recycle Bin, click <strong data-start=\"672\" data-end=\"702\">“Second-stage recycle bin”</strong>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"704\" data-end=\"755\">\n<p data-start=\"706\" data-end=\"755\">Find your item, select it, and click <strong data-start=\"743\" data-end=\"754\">Restore</strong>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 data-start=\"757\" data-end=\"809\">3. <strong data-start=\"765\" data-end=\"809\">Version History (for overwritten files):</strong></h4>\n<ul data-start=\"810\" data-end=\"927\">\n<li data-start=\"810\" data-end=\"860\">\n<p data-start=\"812\" data-end=\"860\">Right-click a file (still present, but changed).</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"861\" data-end=\"890\">\n<p data-start=\"863\" data-end=\"890\">Choose <strong data-start=\"870\" data-end=\"889\">Version history</strong>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"891\" data-end=\"927\">\n<p data-start=\"893\" data-end=\"927\">Restore or view previous versions.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>Restoring Deleted Data in SharePoint (Modern Sites):</h3>\n<h4 data-start=\"998\" data-end=\"1044\"><strong data-start=\"1006\" data-end=\"1044\">From Recycle Bin (within 93 days):</strong></h4>\n<ul data-start=\"1045\" data-end=\"1224\">\n<li data-start=\"1045\" data-end=\"1104\">\n<p data-start=\"1047\" data-end=\"1104\">Go to the <strong data-start=\"1057\" data-end=\"1076\">SharePoint site</strong> where the data was deleted.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1105\" data-end=\"1173\">\n<p data-start=\"1107\" data-end=\"1173\">Click the <strong data-start=\"1117\" data-end=\"1134\">Settings gear</strong> &gt; <strong data-start=\"1137\" data-end=\"1154\">Site contents</strong> &gt; <strong data-start=\"1157\" data-end=\"1172\">Recycle Bin</strong>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1174\" data-end=\"1224\">\n<p data-start=\"1176\" data-end=\"1224\">Select the items you want and click <strong data-start=\"1212\" data-end=\"1223\">Restore</strong>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 data-start=\"1226\" data-end=\"1292\">2. <strong data-start=\"1234\" data-end=\"1292\">Second-Stage Recycle Bin (Site Collection Admin only):</strong></h4>\n<ul data-start=\"1293\" data-end=\"1431\">\n<li data-start=\"1293\" data-end=\"1366\">\n<p data-start=\"1295\" data-end=\"1366\">At the bottom of the Recycle Bin, click <strong data-start=\"1335\" data-end=\"1365\">“Second-stage recycle bin”</strong>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1367\" data-end=\"1431\">\n<p data-start=\"1369\" data-end=\"1431\">Restore deleted files from here if not in the first-stage bin.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 data-start=\"1433\" data-end=\"1466\">3. <strong data-start=\"1441\" data-end=\"1466\">File Version History:</strong></h4>\n<ul data-start=\"1467\" data-end=\"1612\">\n<li data-start=\"1467\" data-end=\"1523\">\n<p data-start=\"1469\" data-end=\"1523\">Navigate to the document library where the file lives.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1524\" data-end=\"1582\">\n<p data-start=\"1526\" data-end=\"1582\">Click the 3 dots next to the file &gt; <strong data-start=\"1562\" data-end=\"1581\">Version history</strong>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"1583\" data-end=\"1612\">\n<p data-start=\"1585\" data-end=\"1612\">Restore a previous version.</p>\n</li>\n</ul></div>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div>\n</div>",
  "sourceUrl": "https://support.dataandmore.com/en/knowledge/deletion-of-data-in-outlook-possible-recovery"
}